headline: Does Realty Income Still Offer Value After Its Recent Share Price Recovery in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether Realty Income is still a high quality dividend name at a fair price, or if most of the value has already been priced in at around $57.44, this article will walk through that question using a clear valuation lens. The stock has quietly climbed 0.7% over the last week and 1.1% over the last month, adding up to a 9.2% gain year to date and 11.5% over the past year.
